entries.femaleVariant: 'Ey, don't you have a test tomorrow? Not gonna study?
Nah, no way I'll get a good grade. Like, why even try, you know?
Can't win against gonks popping the whole damn periodic table just to cram.
But you're sellin' the stuff. Could just pop some yourself.
Yeah, that's why I don't... Anyway, I'm out. Gotta change, dinner at my mom's today.
Yeah, but she brought some of my aunt's old stuff over. Gonna ask why I'm not wearin' it.
Whatta you need hand-me-downs for? You got all that scratch from the merch.
Nah, then she'll give me shit about how I'm too good for everyone.
